      <title>中国被视为英国国防部网络攻击的可能罪魁祸首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-seen-as-likely-culprit-in-uk-defense-ministry-cyberattack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情的英国官员表示，英国武装部队人员在最近的一次网络攻击中获取了个人数据，此次攻击很可能是由中国发起的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-seen-as-likely-culprit-in-uk-defense-ministry-cyberattack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:32:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言铭记美国“公然”轰炸中国大使馆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/xi-vows-to-remember-flagrant-us-bombing-of-chinese-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席誓言“永远不会忘记”北约对中国驻贝尔格莱德大使馆的致命轰炸，数小时后他将穿越欧洲抵达塞尔维亚，旨在分裂布鲁塞尔对美国的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/xi-vows-to-remember-flagrant-us-bombing-of-chinese-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军队控制加沙拉法边境口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-raid-closes-rafah-border-crossing-in-gaza-hamas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队周二早上控制了加沙的拉法过境区，哈马斯表示来自埃及的所有援助均已停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-raid-closes-rafah-border-crossing-in-gaza-hamas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨吹捧以色列法院在南非投票活动中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ramaphosa-touts-israel-court-win-in-south-african-votes-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 正利用其政府结束以色列对哈马斯战争的努力，寻求在唯一一个不受执政党非洲人国民大会控制的省份争取选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ramaphosa-touts-israel-court-win-in-south-african-votes-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新任泰国财政部长表示降息呼声将持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/new-thai-finance-chief-wants-monetary-fiscal-policies-aligned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任财政部长皮查伊·春哈瓦吉拉 (Pichai Chunhavajira) 敦促央行支持政府政策，这表明泰国央行可能会继续面临降息压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/new-thai-finance-chief-wants-monetary-fiscal-policies-aligned</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 03:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度竞选活动变得充满敌意，莫迪和阿达尼投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/modi-s-home-state-votes-in-heated-indian-election-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度第三阶段选举在总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的家乡古吉拉特邦拉开帷幕，两大主要政党之间的竞选活动变得越来越激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/modi-s-home-state-votes-in-heated-indian-election-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克称下次英国大选结果可能比民意调查显示的更接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)表示，下一次英国大选的结果可能比民调显示的结果更接近，这增加了出现悬浮议会、没有任何政党拥有全面控制权的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 18:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平敦促马克龙帮助中国避免“新冷战”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟对安全风险和贸易紧张局势的担忧日益与美国保持一致之际，中国国家主席习近平呼吁法国帮助抵御“新冷战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 17:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯支持的停火计划未能实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯表示已同意加沙地带停火提议，但以色列战时内阁一致拒绝该提议，称其“与以色列的必要要求相去甚远”，这让立即暂停战斗的希望破灭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 16:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举即将进行一半，印度与假新闻作斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/india-battles-fake-news-as-election-heads-to-halfway-mark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着世界上最大规模的选举进入下一阶段，印度正试图打击社交媒体上广泛传播的假新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/india-battles-fake-news-as-election-heads-to-halfway-mark</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
